{"tid":2291658,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"高院：政府要獨立調查 警員需清晰展示警員編號","createTime":"2020-11-19T02:56:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-19T06:56:57.000Z","uid":365024,"like":33,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"aed7a46835ec09eacb30324039dec97233976b75","tid":2291658,"uid":365024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T02:56:29.000Z","msg":"記協及多名市民就去年反修例示威期間，防暴警察及速龍小隊出勤時未有展示警員編號提出司法覆核，高等法院裁定記協、右眼受傷的男教師楊子俊，以及三名在示威中受傷的市叫陳恭信、魯湛思和吳康聯勝訴，裁定警務處處長無法有效確保每名「踏浪者」行動的警員，清晰展示警員編號，違反《香港人權法案》。 <br />\n<br />\n高等法院同時裁定，由投訴警察科處理警員投訴，並由監警會審視的投訴機制，不足以符合《香港人權法案》下，政府要建立獨立調查警員懷疑不當對待投訴機制的要求。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2366922\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2366922&d=VbAd486K8RrC2DEUtq3b5uf4PGxNkgPyFAzKtVao6pc%3D&h=41085028\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2366922</a>"},{"pid":"a737934c31881837613568aeec93517b6b2fec3c","tid":2291658,"uid":8014,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T03:01:01.000Z","msg":"有獨立調查收貨了<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n階段性勝利<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e01332acdf78e285354b7ba7c57c6ed9eeb8d25e","tid":2291658,"uid":65449,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T03:04:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />荒謬判刑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/asse