ji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n節錄唔曬靠巴絲幫我加上去<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/vampire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2810f194a8d8d3b006973d4e88e5078e348593be","tid":2291658,"uid":204539,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T03:05:40.000Z","msg":"冧把有撚用咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff09109fad6cd567d1d64d658ac022229f667250","tid":2291658,"uid":143499,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T03:06:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"575766c4664532b7fb705ec42d4f06669526ee29","tid":2291658,"uid":85924,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T03:10:00.000Z","msg":"高院違反國安法<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1f3bc5c12016bada4b50fcb4288bc80f10d43f2","tid":2291658,"uid":810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T03:10:40.000Z","msg":"依家先黎判 屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45afae0008b463426fb40749bb414a5d0537dc6e","tid":2291658,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T03:11:18.000Z","msg":"警方明知違反人權法都唔會改㗎啦<br />\n你吹得佢漲？"},{"pid":"9a57ca1998d78a70c9ae229a8e1ad9b9d3e92018","tid":2291658,"uid":178875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a737934c31881837613568aeec93517b6b2fec3c","tid":2291658,"uid":8014,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T03:01:01.000Z","msg":"有獨立調查收貨了<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n階段性勝利<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T03:11:55.000Z","msg":"